  "page": "Iggo",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\"><img alt=\"Dothraki.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/50px-Dothraki.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/75px-Dothraki.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/100px-Dothraki.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Iggo</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Brave_Companions\" title=\"Brave Companions\"><img alt=\"Brave Companions.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/Brave_Companions.svg/50px-Brave_Companions.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/24/Brave_Companions.svg/75px-Brave_Companions.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/24/Brave_Companions.svg/100px-Brave_Companions.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Iggo_TheMico.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Iggo TheMico.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c3/Iggo_TheMico.jpg/250px-Iggo_TheMico.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"354\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c3/Iggo_TheMico.jpg/375px-Iggo_TheMico.jpg 1.5x, /images/c/c3/Iggo_TheMico.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Art by The Mico ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Brave_Companions\" title=\"Brave Companions\">Brave Companions</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Iggo</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Brave_Companions\" title=\"Brave Companions\">Brave Companions</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Iggo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Iggo is scarred. He wears bells in his hair and uses an <i><a href=\"/index.php/Arakh\" title=\"Arakh\">arakh</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Iggo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Iggo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Iggo and three other <a href=\"/index.php/Brave_Companions\" title=\"Brave Companions\">Brave Companions</a>—a pale <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lyseni</a>, an <a href=\"/index.php/Ibbenese\" title=\"Ibbenese\">Ibbenese</a> axeman, and a <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishman</a>—search for Nan (actually <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a>), <a href=\"/index.php/Gendry\" title=\"Gendry\">Gendry</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Hot_Pie\" title=\"Hot Pie\">Hot Pie</a> after they escape from <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>. While sleeping, Arya <a href=\"/index.php/Skinchanger\" title=\"Skinchanger\">dreams</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria_(direwolf)\" title=\"Nymeria (direwolf)\">a wolf</a> hunting the sellswords as they pursue the youths in the rain. The three other Brave Companions die quickly when her <a href=\"/index.php/Wolf\" title=\"Wolf\">wolfpack</a> attacks, but Iggo's horse kicks in the head of one wolf and the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> uses his <i><a href=\"/index.php/Arakh\" title=\"Arakh\">arakh</a></i> to kill another. The great wolf leading them leaps onto Iggo's back to knock him from the saddle. Tearing off his arm, she shakes it and sends blood flying through the rain.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Iggo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Only the belled man stood his ground. His horse kicked in the head of one of <a href=\"/index.php/Wolf\" title=\"Wolf\">her sisters</a>, and he cut another almost in half with <a href=\"/index.php/Arakh\" title=\"Arakh\">his curved silvery claw</a> as his hair tinkled softly.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya</a>'s thoughts when <a href=\"/index.php/Skinchanger\" title=\"Skinchanger\">dreaming</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria_(direwolf)\" title=\"Nymeria (direwolf)\">Nymeria</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Iggo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_3\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 3\">Chapter 3</a>, Arya I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403232529\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.140 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.661 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 574/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10561/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6642/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 888/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1059/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.330/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.57 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  620.995      1 -total\n 97.59%  606.034      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 97.25%  603.911      1 Template:Infobox\n  9.79%   60.786     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  2.87%   17.809      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.64%   16.379      1 Template:Date\n  1.72%   10.674      3 Template:Ref\n  1.05%    6.536      3 Template:Ref/core\n  0.49%    3.016    